channel.title: Is there any reason my height changes?
channel.description: i try to tele anywhere and it changes my height. except when i tele to home. but it wasnt doing that a minute ago. i teleported to castle wars and then tried to tele home but my height was like 3. so i deleted my account and made another one and now whenever i tele anywhere except home my height will go up. any ideas?

item.title: Is there any reason my height changes?
item.dc:creator: @j19283746 j19283746
item.description:
@j19283746 wrote:

Find the commands you used to get to the place where it changed your height. It would say like

teleportToX = 1000;
teleportToY = 2000;
heightLevel = 3;
Change the 3 to 0 if you want to be on the ground.

Read full topic
